data.description: Introducing a fantastic 1943 sqft living space, 4-bedroom, 2-bath, 2-car garage with an open floor plan, with great natural lighting. It's located in the charming Cypress Cay community within Gateway. This delightful residence was   given a complete facelift in 2023, including new roof, bathroom and kitchen remodeling, flooring, and all new appliances.  Seller is including $5,000 to buyer at closing in addition to a one-year home warranty at sellers cost, which will provide you an added layer of peace. Cypress Cay is not only charming and a quiet neighborhood, but also a close-knit community located in a very good school district. Additionally, it is only 10-15 minutes from SW Intl Airport, Gulf Coast Town Ctr, and Gulf Coast Medical Ctr. It has low HOA fees and is in no flood zone! Don't miss the opportunity to own this great property. Furniture not included in the sale of home but is negotiable.
